I have made over 500ml of this and it is easily my ADV. I am all for exploring new flavors and recipes but i find I need a baseline to return to when stuff is off or weird or simply not my thing. This has a nice subtle flavor to it i have mixed it several ways. It just works and I love it. I've mixed this at 70/30 and 60/40, i mixed this with low nic and high nic. it doesn't matter. the biggest thing that will make a difference is you can SAV it but it really becomes something wonderful after 7 days. You don't have OoO Cream take the plunge buy it in the 4 oz bottle (only option I had when I bought it) and don't look back. Thank you Fear for another solid recipe. this needs to be sold as a flavor pack on BCF if they could get OoO Cream that is.&#xD;
&#xD;
UPDATE 11/26/19 This has been in my rotation for a couple years. Its so good. Thank you Fear
